| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0707 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1e9112dc-9c3e-53d9-8ea6-bb9332eb89c3"
